幕底部弹出的笨重下载栏（并且必须自行关闭它）。今后，下载内容将显示在浏览器的右上角，就在您的帐户图像旁边。当您要保存某些内容时，图标周围会出现一个圆圈，下载完成后会变成蓝色。您可以单击该按钮查看过去 24 小时内保存的任何内容，打开包含特定文件的文件夹并重试、暂停、恢复或取消下载。虽然这将是每个人前进的默认位置，但它可能已经对某些人来说已经上线了。如果下载看起来可疑，Google 仍会向您发出警告，并允许您根据需要拖放下载。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/googles-chrome-updates-bring-improved-search-to-mobile-and-simler-desktop-downloads-160003908.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/googles-chrome-updates-bring-improved-search-to-mobile-and-simpler-desktop-downloads-160003908.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 98fcdced-3172-4dcc-ae0c-56844c1a8972</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 02 Aug 2023 16:00:03 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690973572</ingested><modified> 2023-08-02T10:52:55+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="500" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/fbec99e0-3117-11ee-beb7-d4085ca3163e" width="1200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="500" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/fbec99e0-3117-11ee-beb7-d4085ca3163e" width="1200"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Google]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A cartoon p